nodes.text: The Imperial Space Station was a space station in the Kashyyyk system operated by the Galactic Empire during the time of the Galactic Civil War. It was staffed by a Zabrak Imperial.

The Imperial Space Station was a location in Rage of the Wookiees, the 2005 expansion pack for the massively multiplayer online role-playing game Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided, prior to the game's closure on December 15, 2011.
